{"tid":1669801,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[台灣法律]「自首」是犯案後，未被發覺之前，自願申告自己之犯罪事實","createTime":"2019-10-22T18:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T18:52:09.000Z","uid":103207,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe40d404790f1638cddc0907815a34a60c0c9f1","tid":1669801,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T18:22:39.000Z","msg":"根據台灣法律網指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">「自首」是指犯刑罰之罪</span>，不論是故意犯或過失犯，<span style=\"color: red;\">在未被發覺之前，自願向該管機關申告自己之犯罪事實</span>。而若是<span style=\"color: red;\">犯罪者在該管公務員已經發覺犯罪事實並已懷疑為某人所犯後</span>，才自動到案者，<span style=\"color: red;\">僅得以「投案」論，並非自首。</span><br />\n<br />\n台灣法律唔同香港,唔係冇罪推定,一日未宣判前認罪都當自首<br />\n警察一將你當嫌疑犯後,已經冇得自首<br />\n<br />\nRIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a39b06663387e6b7cd4c880541540c30951599f","tid":1669801,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T18:52:09.000Z","msg":"條弱智綠帽仔<br />\n下次可以揀個好d既地方 殺潘金蓮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然可能已經冇下一次"}]}